videos.headline: Tennessee finds the end zone first
videos.description: Carlin Fils-aime rushes one yard into the end zone for a Volunteers touchdown vs. Missouri.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Tennessee finds the end zone first) 2019/11/23

videos.headline: Missouri scores TD for first time in 33 possessions
videos.description: Missouri's touchdown in the first half vs. Tennessee breaks the longest streak without an offensive touchdown in college football.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Missouri scores TD for first time in 33 possessions) 2019/11/23

videos.headline: Jennings dodges multiple tackles for Vols TD
videos.description: Jarrett Guarantano connects with Jauan Jennings for a 16-yard touchdown to put Tennessee up 14-10 vs. Missouri.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Jennings dodges multiple tackles for Vols TD) 2019/11/23

videos.headline: Badie hauls in wide-open 15-yard TD for Missouri
videos.description: Micah Wilson finds Tyler Badie in the end zone for a 15-yard touchdown to tie Tennessee at 17-17.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Badie hauls in wide-open 15-yard TD for Missouri) 2019/11/23

videos.headline: Missouri blocks Tennessee's FG attempt
videos.description: Brent Cimaglia's 48-yard field goal attempt is blocked by Missouri's Devin Nicholson and return for 14 yards to the Tennessee 41-yard line.

videos.headline: Tennessee's Callaway makes a nice catch for TD
videos.description: Jarrett Guarantano connects with Marquez Callaway, who makes a nice catch in the end zone under pressure to put the Vols up in the third quarter.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Tennessee's Callaway makes a nice catch for TD) 2019/11/23
